      "content": "that's an interesting way to look at it. \"points of concentrated power\" is a pretty heavy phrase though. i was looking at the specific way the angles hit the corner of 4th and Broadway in nyc and then compared it to the alignment of the obelisks in london. the math is almost too tight to be just \"natural energy.\" it feels more like someone was following a specific blueprint. if they were using these lines to funnel something, where do you think the nodes actually lead?",
